        <Parent_String>amber (fossil resin) [300012934], fossil resin [300012933], resin (organic material) [300012882], organic material [300011792], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
